        "source": "X85n1594_006:0572c08_30",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無我我故。",
        "translation": "It's because there's no self and self.",
        "source": "X85n1594_006:0572c08_31",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無我我故。",
        "translation": "Because there's no self and self, it means the mind doesn't arise and cease.",
        "source": "X85n1594_006:0572c09_32",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
